2. The 4th day of June 2021 is appointed as the day on which the Loan 
Guarantee Schemes Agreements (Strategic Banking Corporation of Ireland) Act 
2021 (No. 9 of 2021) shall come into operation. 

GIVEN under my Official Seal, 

31 May, 2021. 

LEO VARADKAR, 

Minister for Enterprise, Trade and Employment. 

Notice of the making of this Statutory Instrument was published in 
“Iris Oifigiúil” of 4th June, 2021.

EXPLANATORY NOTE 

(This is not part of the Instrument and does not purport to be a legal 
interpretation.) 

This Order appoints 4th of June 2021 as the date on which the Loan Guarantee 
Schemes Agreements (Strategic Banking Corporation of Ireland) Act 2021 
comes into operation.
